com.bosch.security.codecs

Class HashTrie<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bosch.security.codecs.HashTrie<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Trie<T>, java.util.Map<java.lang.CharSequence,T>

    public class HashTrie<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Trie<T>
    Trie implementation for CharSequence keys. This uses HashMaps for each level instead of the traditional array. This is done as with unicode, each level's array would be 64k entries.
